            </div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Result:</span> Use
              <span class="font-semibold text-amber-600">1-1/4&quot; Schedule 40 IPS</span> for the main trunk. The
              1-1/4&quot; pipe has 289,000 BTU/h capacity at 50 ft, giving a 61% safety margin above the
